游戏都有「角色受到伤害之后一段时间内无敌」这样的设定。但这是为什么？毕竟 3D 游戏中就几乎不存在这种设定。 我个人的理解是，相比于 3D 游戏，2D 游戏相对更强调玩家在有限的 2D 空间内精确运动，因此早期 2D 游戏通常会引入碰撞伤害这类设定以逼迫玩家在空间里动起来。而在这种情况下，如果不加入受击保护的话，主角很有可能会被连续的碰撞伤害直接多次判定给秒杀。 且 2D 游戏或多或少会存在一些平台跳跃要素，一旦玩家跌入陷阱，那就需要重置位置和摄像机，而在重制之后如果没有受击保护，那就容易出现「跌入陷阱 - 重置 - 挨打 - 跌入陷阱 -…」这样的循环。 问题抛砖引玉，看看各位的理解"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-548cb378792f64ff36f04dd670701729_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661836585"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip9rBsej8pvQREAMaCTEwOTM1MjY2OCC5t920BjAAODFAJXIJNjYxODM2NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1721686710.623705", "card_id": "Q_662301694", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "詹姆斯将成为美国奥运代表团开幕式旗手，创 NBA 历史，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-51d30e36179354687c06f4a2be8e0c60_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662301694"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip9rBsej8pvQREAMaCTEwOTQ1NTk5OCDqi/m0BjAAOG5AJnIJNjYyMzAxNjk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1721686710.623867", "card_id": "Q_661343991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "端侧模型 + 硬件会是 AI 爆发的下一个机会吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661343991"}}, "atta